I created a new proposal about participant registration improvement in STL. <https://jira.hyperledger.org/projects/STL/issues/STL-11?filter=allopenissues> 
Any comments are welcome. :slightly_smiling_face:
<@U1ZUSJHAA> Thanks for submitting the proposal! We'll take a look at it.
<@U1ZUSJHAA> - I don't think we have an official logo
<@U1ZUSJHAA> - is your proposal specific to to mktplace?

<@U0YQQRNU8> The process I described in proposal is for the participant register in mktplace , However, I think the method can be applied to other  transaction families that include such identity management .  for example, XoTransaction.
